cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "zzcollab: Docker-based Reproducible Research Collaboration Framework"
version: 0.9.2
date-released: "2026-06-01"
license: GPL-3.0-or-later
repository-code: "https://github.com/rgt47/zzcollab"
abstract: >
  zzcollab is a turnkey framework for reproducible research collaboration
  using Docker containers. It generates research compendiums with pinned
  R environments (renv), content-addressed base images, dated Posit Package
  Manager snapshots, and team collaboration workflows. The package provides
  both a command-line scaffold tool and an R interface for managing
  containerised analysis environments.
authors:
